operations.name: leerGenero
operations.filter: from LibroEN as l where l.Genero= :genero

operations.name: leerUsuario
operations.filter: from LibroEN as l inner join l.Usuario as u where u.Nombre = :usuario

operations.name: leerPrecio
operations.filter: from LibroEN as l where l.Precio= :precio

operations.name: leerNombre
operations.filter: from LibroEN as l where l.Nombre= :nombre

operations.name: leerTitulo
operations.filter: from CriticaEN as c where c.Titulo = :p_titulo

operations.name: leerNombre
operations.filter: from AlbumEN as a where a.Titulo= :titulo

operations.name: leerNombre
operations.filter: from UsuarioEN as u where u.Nombre = :nombre

operations.name: leerEmail
operations.filter: from UsuarioEN as u where u.Email = :email

operations.name: leerNombre
operations.filter: from AutorEN as aut where aut.Nombre = :nombre

operations.name: leerNombre
operations.filter: from PublicacionEN as p where p.Nombre =:nombre
